<div class="grid-row">
    <div class="column-two-thirds">
        <h1 class="heading-xlarge">Change apprentice details</h1>

        <p>A request will be sent to &lt;Defence Ministry&gt; to approve the following change in the apprenticeship service.</p>

        <table>
            <thead>
                <tr>
